Definition: a Buddhist and Hindu and especially Jainist doctrine holding that all forms of life are sacred and urging the avoidance of violence
Synonyms: religious_doctrine, noun, cognition, Buddhism, c, Hinduism, Jainism, a, Buddhist, and, Hindu, especially, Jainist, doctrine, holding, that, all, forms, of, life, are, sacred, urging, the, avoidance, violence
Category: noun.communication
